'''盧克·阿諾德'''（'''Luke Arnold'''，{{bd|1984年}}）是[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]的一位演員。他出生在阿德萊德，小學時和家人搬家到雪梨<ref name=debelle>{{cite news|last1=Debelle|first1=Penelope|title=INXS miniseries star and Adelaide actor Luke Arnold uses rising fame to help kids|url=http://www.adelaidenow.com.au/entertainment/inxs-miniseries-star-and-adelaide-actor-luke-arnold-uses-rising-fame-to-help-kids/story-fni6umbp-1226834534180?nk=9a72055e8fa0b647b08eb674311468b3|accessdate=9 September 2014|work=The Advertiser|date=22 February 2014|archive-date=2014-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140910212307/http://www.adelaidenow.com.au/entertainment/inxs-miniseries-star-and-adelaide-actor-luke-arnold-uses-rising-fame-to-help-kids/story-fni6umbp-1226834534180?nk=9a72055e8fa0b647b08eb674311468b3|dead-url=no}}</ref>，之後又搬至昆士蘭。他出演過[[小飛俠彼得潘_(電影)|小飛俠彼得潘]]等電影<ref name=interview>Brown, Emma: [http://www.interviewmagazine.com/culture/discovery-luke-arnold#_ Discovery: Luke Arnold] {{Wayback|url=http://www.interviewmagazine.com/culture/discovery-luke-arnold#_ |date=20180522103140 }}, ''Interview'', January 2014.</ref>。

